You have created a server-side function.  It is useful for `y = f(x)` type of operations only.   You cannot create &quot;stored procs&quot; like an agg pipeline in your example.
What you can do is create a view:
```
db.createView(
&quot;myView&quot;,
&quot;People&quot;,
[
 {$lookup: {
                from: &quot;Role&quot;,
                localField: &quot;RoleId&quot;,
                foreignField : &quot;_id&quot;,
                as: &quot;Role&quot;
            }
 }
]
              );

```
and now you can use `myView` like a collection, e.g.
```
db.myView.find();
db.myView.aggregate(yourPipelinehere);
```

